                              my baby you'll be.`;
        audioButtons.style.display = "flex";
    } else if (bookSelector.value === "threeblindmice") {
        bookImage.src = "book-threeblindmice.png";
        bookText.innerText = `“ Three Blind Mice
                                Three Blind Mice
                                See how they run
